{"id": "EUVD-2024-28184", "enisaUuid": "66dd1416-4748-3b2e-93f2-7b64845b8da1", "description": "FastDDS is a C++ implementation of the DDS (Data Distribution Service) standard of the OMG (Object Management Group). Prior to versions 2.14.1, 2.13.5, 2.10.4, and 2.6.8, when a publisher serves a malformed `RTPS` packet, the subscriber crashes when creating `pthread`. This can remotely crash any Fast-DDS process, potentially leading to a DOS attack. Versions 2.14.1, 2.13.5, 2.10.4, and 2.6.8 contain a patch for the issue.\n", "datePublished": "2024-05-13T14:41:52", "dateUpdated": "2024-08-02T01:32:05", "baseScore": 8.2, "baseScoreVersion": "3.1", "baseScoreVector": "CVSS:3.1/AV:N/AC:L/PR:N/UI:N/S:U/C:N/I:L/A:H", "references": ["https://github.com/eProsima/Fast-DDS/security/advisories/GHSA-53xw-465j-rxfh", "https://github.com/eProsima/Fast-DDS/commit/65236f93e9c4ea3ff9a49fba4dfd9e43eb94037b", "https://drive.google.com/file/d/19W5UC52hPnAqVq_boZWO45d1TJ4WoCSh/view?usp=sharing"], "aliases": ["CVE-2024-30258"], "assigner": "GitHub_M", "epss": 1.3, "enisaIdProduct": [{"id": "3dcf1758-3c75-3cc1-93e3-2b2a286bfe7c", "product": {"name": "Fast-DDS"}, "product_version": "= 2.14.0"}, {"id": "63ab1f16-231f-3fd3-aa02-9b56eaa1bb2f", "product": {"name": "Fast-DDS"}, "product_version": "2.10.0, < 2.10.4"}, {"id": "a12c357b-4479-3b60-8499-1a699f7a6341", "product": {"name": "Fast-DDS"}, "product_version": "< 2.6.8"}, {"id": "e1690ecf-fa62-34f5-ac5f-57a4edfd8ecb", "product": {"name": "Fast-DDS"}, "product_version": "2.13.0, < 2.13.5"}], "enisaIdVendor": [{"id": "80978642-dfd1-3d72-b501-23d461d45ea9", "vendor": {"name": "eProsima"}}], "isExploited": false}